* **CSS Selectors:** [MDN Web Docs - CSS Selectors](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Selectors)
* **Unicode Characters:** [Unicode Character Table](https://unicode-table.com/en/)


